search_by_name.notes: Single GET parameter q (label: 'Que recherchez-vous ?'). Typical usage: /bruxelles?q=restaurant

profile_by_id.notes: Thread/post numeric ID appears in URL path like /bruxelles/94523080 or /bruxelles/50472732 (slug component optional)

route_search.notes: Primary inputs are start (start) and end (end). Autocomplete suggestion fields are start_suggestion and end_suggestion. There are separate fields for date (new_departure_datetime[date]) and time (new_departure_datetime[time]).

route_search_date.notes: Date is provided in an HTML date input (ISO format YYYY-MM-DD).

route_search_time.notes: Time is provided in an HTML time input (HH:MM).

start_or_arrival.notes: Radio selecting departure vs arrival semantics.

disabled.notes: Checkbox to search with accessibility/disabled-friendly options.
